Message:
Those words echo in my
mind over and over again.

I should be scared
to death of this crown,
so why can’t I just
let go of it...?

I felt as if someone was
calling out my name.
But, who...?

It’s someone who’s
as bright as the sun.
Someone who always
fills me with courage...

That’s right. I’ve been
waiting for this moment.

The moment when you
come and save me...

“I’ve come to keep my promise.
Let’s go home, Priscilla.
Together.”

Huh? How strange.
I can’t get my words
to come out,

even though there
are so many things
I wanted to say.

But now,
I’ll say the words
I want to tell you
the most.
